#: packages/core/admin-ui/src/pages/OptInDetailPage.tsx:252
msgid ""
"Reset this opt-in to PENDING for re-testing?\n"
"\n"
"This is a DEV-ONLY action (WP_DEBUG mode). It clears the confirmation flag so you can click the same email link again.\n"
"\n"
"Note: any Avada submissions/entries written by the previous confirmation are kept — delete them via Avada's Form Entries UI if you need a clean slate.\n"
"\n"
"Files: any uploaded files were already handed off to the form system or sent as mail attachments at the previous confirmation, so they are NOT restored. Re-submit the form if you want files in the next test cycle."
msgstr ""
"Réinitialiser cet opt-in sur EN ATTENTE pour un nouveau test ?\n"
"\n"
"Ceci est une action RÉSERVÉE AU DÉVELOPPEMENT (mode WP_DEBUG). Elle efface l'indicateur de confirmation afin que vous puissiez cliquer à nouveau sur le même lien d'e-mail.\n"
"\n"
